# Cooked room blobs and texture blobs land here via
# `cook-playtest` / the editor's "Cook & Play" action. They're
# a deterministic function of the editor's project state and
# easy to regenerate — committing them would just churn diffs
# every time someone cooks. The committed `level_manifest.rs`
# is in placeholder state (zero rooms / zero textures) so the
# example still compiles without these files.
rooms/*.psxw
textures/*.psxt
